a Mexican burrito.

14:52.892 --> 14:55.383
Are you sure that's the best
thing for you right now?

14:55.461 --> 14:57.827
Oh, it's the best thing
on the menu.

14:58.397 --> 15:00.297
So, look, I feel
like I may have

15:00.432 --> 15:02.366
gone a little off message
at the pit.

15:02.434 --> 15:03.492
Yeah, you seemed
a little weird.

15:03.569 --> 15:04.558
Well, I wouldn't say weird.

15:04.637 --> 15:07.629
