community park

15:10.442 --> 15:14.606
and a positive article could go a
long way towards making that happen.

15:14.680 --> 15:15.669
Great.

15:15.748 --> 15:19.980
So what do you think the odds are that
this park is actually gonna get made?

15:20.052 --> 15:24.546
