where the Pope can be married.

15:58.290 --> 16:00.224
"You should write an article
on talking monkeys."

16:00.292 --> 16:01.418
Really? Have you seen
<i>The Wizard of Oz?</i>

16:01.493 --> 16:03.427
"You should write an article
about leprechauns."

16:03.495 --> 16:04.587
Leprechauns exist.

16:04.663 --> 16:07.427
"You should write an article about
the sun falling out of the sky."

16:07.499 --> 16:09.694
Why would you write an
article about that? That's...

16:09.768 --> 16:11.668
This one is just "No."

16:13.472 --> 16:17.841
"This park is never, ever, ever,
ever going to happen."

16:20.913 --> 16:22.437
Might I ask
who said that?

16:22.514 --> 16:24.209
Mark Brendanawicz.

16:28.754 --> 16:29.778
(KNOCKING AT DOOR)

16:29.855 --> 16:31.220
Yeah.
Hey.

16:31.657 --> 16:32.646
Hi.

16:32.725 --> 16:34.249
Can I talk to you
for a second?

16:34.326 --> 16:35.816
Yeah, what's up?

16:35.894 --> 16:39.990
You and I need to find a way
to fix this reporter thing.

16:40.532 --> 16:42.466
