17:09.795 --> 17:10.989
Hey, Mark.

17:11.063 --> 17:12.462
Hey.

17:12.531 --> 17:13.656
Uh...

17:14.266 --> 17:15.858
I heard that you were gonna
print some of that stuff

17:15.934 --> 17:17.992
