17:23.776 --> 17:24.765
'cause we're trying
to build this park...

17:24.843 --> 17:25.935
I don't understand.

17:26.011 --> 17:28.172
You did say it, right?

17:28.247 --> 17:29.475
Technically.

17:29.548 --> 17:31.015
Technically?

17:31.083 --> 17:33.244
Well, you know,

17:33.318 --> 17:35.684
you got up because you had to
write the article and I said,

17:35.754 --> 17:37.745
"Come on,
stay in bed.

17:37.823 --> 17:40.690
"That park is never, ever,
ever gonna get made."

17:40.759 --> 17:43.227
Right. And then
I came back to bed.

17:43.295 --> 17:47.026
Yeah, but the important part of
what I said was, "Stay in bed."

17:47.099 --> 17:49.533
You know,
I would've said anything at that point

17:49.601 --> 17:51.330
if I thought it would
make you stay in bed.

17:51.403 --> 17:52.700
(CHUCKLES)

17:52.771 --> 17:56.070
Okay, well, since we're,
you know, romantically involved,

17:56.141 --> 17:57.574
I won't print any of it.

17:57.643 --> 17:59.543
That's great. Thank you so much.
You're welcome.

17:59.611 --> 18:03.513
You know, I wouldn't say
romantically involved.

18:03.582 --> 18:05.675
You know,
going forward.

18:07.186 --> 18:08.619
